### ── CUSTOMER PORTAL SERVICE (/catalog) ────────────────────────────────────
### Environment: Ctrl+Shift+P → Rest Client: Switch Environment → dev

### 1. List catalog — unauthenticated (anonymous)
GET {{baseUrl}}/catalog/Vehicles

### 2. List catalog — as Customer
GET {{baseUrl}}/catalog/Vehicles
Authorization: {{customerBauerAuth}}

### 3. Single vehicle detail — Porsche 911
GET {{baseUrl}}/catalog/Vehicles/40000000-4000-4000-4000-400000000005
Authorization: {{customerBauerAuth}}

### 4. Vehicle images — Porsche 911
GET {{baseUrl}}/catalog/VehicleImages?$filter=vehicle_ID eq 40000000-4000-4000-4000-400000000005
Authorization: {{customerBauerAuth}}

### 5. Price history — Porsche 911 (seed data available)
GET {{baseUrl}}/catalog/getPriceHistory(vehicleId='40000000-4000-4000-4000-400000000005')
Authorization: {{customerBauerAuth}}

### 6. Filter — electric vehicles only
GET {{baseUrl}}/catalog/Vehicles?$filter=fuelType eq 'ELECTRIC'
Authorization: {{customerBauerAuth}}

### 7. Filter — BMW brand vehicles
GET {{baseUrl}}/catalog/Vehicles?$filter=brand eq 'BMW'
Authorization: {{customerBauerAuth}}

### 8. Filter — price range (30,000–60,000 EUR)
GET {{baseUrl}}/catalog/Vehicles?$filter=price ge 30000 and price le 60000
Authorization: {{customerBauerAuth}}

### 9. Sort — by price ascending
GET {{baseUrl}}/catalog/Vehicles?$orderby=price asc
Authorization: {{customerBauerAuth}}

### 10. Pagination — first 5 vehicles
GET {{baseUrl}}/catalog/Vehicles?$top=5&$skip=0
Authorization: {{customerBauerAuth}}

### 11. Get favorites — Customer Bauer (should return empty list if none)
GET {{baseUrl}}/catalog/getFavoriteVehicles()
Authorization: {{customerBauerAuth}}
